This is how to count_upper of s:
  Remember that count is 0
  Remember that found is no
  Do this s's length times:
    When found is yes, then:
      Leave the loop
    End when
    Remember that i is diff of s's length and count
    Decrease i
    Remember that ch is item i in s
    When ch is at least 65, then:
      When ch is at most 90, then:
        Increase count
      But, if not:
        Remember that found is yes
      End when
    But, if not:
      Remember that found is yes
    End when
  End do
  The answer is count
